  <brief_title>Endoscopic Resection of Bladder Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endoscopic Rescetion of High Grade(TA, T1, Cis)Non-muscle Invasive Bladder Tumors: Modification of Usual Management of This Resection by Using the Blue Light and Evaluation of the Outcome: Should we Maintain the Dogma of Second Endoscopic Resection as a Principle?</official_title>
