  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - 18 year-old and older male and female subjects having high grade non-muscle invasive
        bladder tumor, with urinary cytology , imaging examination (Ultrasound, urography, or
        scan) and endoscopic examination

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - Less than 18 years of age, and having no:

          -  Non-muscle invasive tumor, and of low grade.

          -  Bladder tumor infiltrating the muscular layer shown by pre-operative test, with
             absence of urinary cytology

          -  No blue light source in sustainable way
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
